messages.message: There’s a change to the design of this page where we’re showing the Explore and Apps buttons now, before this wasn’t there. Is it an intended change?
This is intended. We want to allow guest users to see the public apps, so now the apps tab is always visible even if the user is not logged in
I think that makes sense on the home page, but before when entering your MFA code it was blank before this release, as if you click one of the buttons it takes you out of the login flow
